ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.

WVRPS by WarpSound (Official)
collection.description:
WVRPS are the 1st hybrid generative PFP + AI-composed music NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain. 9,999 unique NFTs based on the WarpSound virtual artists Nayomi, Gnar Heart + DJ Dragoon, with art by Emmy-winning illustrator Andy Poon, the embedded 1/1 original music composed entirely by AI using the visual traits of the PFP 🤯

WVRPS are the opening note of WarpSound’s larger vision for interactive, social music experience, helping ignite the future of generative music creativity + synthetic artistry. 🚀

https://warpsound.ai

detail.name: WVRP #8091
detail.description: WVRPS is a collection of 9,999 virtual artist NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain and derived from WarpSound's OG triad of metaverse creators: Nayomi, DJ Dragoon and Gnar Heart. Each audiovisual WVRP is a unique fusion of generative visual PFP art and original music composed and produced by WarpSound's AI-driven audio engine. WVRPS is the opening note of WarpSound's greater vision for generative music creativity and social music experience. Each WVRP is a singular key to a deeper connection with music.

ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.
